parts.text:
Batch-script 
{
"application": "Batch-script",
"details": "This script is used for automatic generation and submission of batch-job files for various batch queuing systems such as qsub, msub, and LoadLeveler.\nIt supports a wide range of computing clusters and systems including IBM, HLRN, CSC Helsinki, DKRZ, and many more. \nIt offers options to set the job catalog, job name, memory demand, CPU time, and more. It also allows for specifying the remote host, username, and queue to use.\nThe script includes features like error handling, confirmation prompts, and automatic dayfile transfer to the local host after job completion.",
"resource_requirements": [
"qsub",
"msub",
"LoadLeveler",
"scp",
"ssh",
"batch_scp",
"ftpcopy"
]
}
